  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Notes</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Butter and pudding are delicious. When you enter the game and see the developer logo (when Nakukinoko appears): press N+K (keyboard) at the same time to unlock the sweet fruit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/57e0e0de351e8f2d63f2407acb3b7606.avif?t=1766152309\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Introduction：</strong><br><br>\"Survivor Girls of Monster Dungeon\" is a 2.5D adventure game featuring roguelike survival gameplay. You'll navigate randomly generated maps, aiding several charming girls in defeating hordes of monsters to survive in perilous dungeons.<br><br><strong>Feature</strong><br><br>Over a dozen adorable girls of various professions must pick up weapons to protect themselves and strive to survive in this dangerous dungeon filled with various monsters! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/6b3c014cd7502c50cd9213f1d2439492.poster.avif?t=1766152309\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/6b3c014cd7502c50cd9213f1d2439492.webm?t=1766152309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/6b3c014cd7502c50cd9213f1d2439492.mp4?t=1766152309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose different branching paths to devise more diverse strategies. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/a4bd385e3f28083466496150f507609c.poster.avif?t=1766152309\" width=640 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/a4bd385e3f28083466496150f507609c.webm?t=1766152309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/a4bd385e3f28083466496150f507609c.mp4?t=1766152309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Real-time dynamic skeletal animation ensures more delicate and detailed performances.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/e2e7f84fc68879f3dda30459969ecbfc.poster.avif?t=1766152309\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/e2e7f84fc68879f3dda30459969ecbfc.webm?t=1766152309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147510/extras/e2e7f84fc68879f3dda30459969ecbfc.mp4?t=1766152309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
